Telah dilaksanakan Webinar Series SRExRM dari tanggal 10 - 14 Agustus 2020 dengan total peserta lebih dari 15 ribu peserta, berikut video dokumentasi Webinar Series SRExRM! 

Terimakasih atas antusias kalian yang sangat besar!
Langkah dan skill yang harus dimiliki oleh anak muda saat ini bareng Duta SGDs Indonesia Ka Vania Herlambang

[𝑰𝒏𝒅𝒐𝒏𝒆𝒔𝒊𝒂 𝑾𝒊𝒍𝒍 𝑯𝒂𝒗𝒆 𝒂 𝑵𝒖𝒄𝒍𝒆𝒂𝒓 𝑷𝒐𝒘𝒆𝒓 𝑷𝒍𝒂𝒏𝒕??] 
Did you know that Indonesia is planning to build a nuclear power plant for the future?

Empowering the future: Indonesia’s visionary step towards sustainable energy with the upcoming nuclear power plant🌍⚛️ 

Soon, Indonesia is planning to have a Nuclear Power Plant which is a project run by ThorCon Power Indonesia targeted to operate in 2030 and is rumored to be built in the Bangka Belitung Islands.
So, let’s deepen our knowledge about RE by checking out the information we provide and create a positive impact on our world.

#FunFact #RenewableEnergy #SRE #SREITB #SREIndonesia #NuclearEnergy #IndonesiaPower

Greetings, Energizen! 

Have you ever heard about 𝘙𝘦𝘥𝘰𝘹 𝘍𝘭𝘰𝘸 𝘉𝘢𝘵𝘵𝘦𝘳𝘺 ?
RFB is an electrochemical system where electrical energy is stored within two solutions containing different redox pairs. 
So, Why was this topic brought up? Can Indonesia initiate this? What is Indonesia’s potential in this aspect? Let’s swipe for more! ☀️🍃

#RenewableEnergy
#SRE
#SREITB

🍃⚡ Plans and Strategies for Energy Transition in Indonesia 🍃⚡

Greetings, Youth of Renewable Energy! 🌱

Do you know that Indonesia has a net-zero emissions target by 2060. To achieve that, Indonesia must accelerate its energy transition by making some impactful steps. So, what plans and strategies does Indonesia make and what can we do to support the energy transition in our country?
Swipe left to find out❗️

#RenewableEnergy #EnergyTransition #SRE #SREITB #SREIndonesia #SocietyofRenewableEnergy #SocietyofRenewableEnergyITB

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Society of Renewable Energy on December 19, 2023. May be a Twitter screenshot of poster and text that says 'sRe Institut Teknologi Bandung Energy Transition Situation in Indonesia Menurut data... Menurut data Kementerian Energi dan Sumber Daya Mineral (ESDM), saat ini bauran energi primer Indonesia masih didominasi oleh fosil. Tenaga Ahli Menteri ESDM, Sripeni Inten Cahyani, mengatakan bauran energi primer dari batu bara dan minyak bumi pada 2023 mencapai 74 persen, sedangkan porsi EBT sekitar 12,3 persen. sre.co.id/teams/sre-itb SRE SREITB ITB sreitb'.

Photo by Society of Renewable Energy on December 19, 2023. May be an image of magazine, plant and text that says 'sRe Institut Teknologi Bandung Plans for Energy Transition in Indonesia Sebagai agenda nasional, transisi energi di Indonesia saat ini in merupakan upaya menjaga ketahanan energi dan mewujudkan ekonomi hijau di Indonesia. Menteri Koordinator Bidang Perekonomian, Airlangga Hartarto, dalam wawancaranya pada Januari 2023 menyampaikan bahwa Pemerintah telah meningkatkan target komposisi Energi Baru dan Terbarukan dalam bauran energi menjadi: 23% pada tahun 2025 31% pada tahun 2050 sre.co.id/teams/sre-itb SREITB sreitb'.
